metadata.name: HEAD_01
metadata.description:
This work aims to a conversion of traditional portraits.

The pictorial expression of the person gives way to a form between the real and the digital. They are avatars of representation that modify the shapes and features of the individual, adapting to a new space and a new survival. If before the attempt was made to remove the psyche from the model, now that psyche is masked. We live and offer ourselves in this masquerade ball.
